  "YangsThoughts": "Like most Warhammer variants the 7S can perform at any range, not phenomenally but if the backbone of your forces is a jack of all trades it's easier to work around. The double heat sinks help keep the ER PPCs fed with cooling and the rest of the weaponry mean getting in punching range of a 7S not a wise choice either. The main design floor in my opinion is putting the unprotected streak ammo in the Center Torso."
